{"tid":1998220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃色經濟圈標籤化，咁本土經濟圈又如何？","createTime":"2020-05-02T08:42:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T03:03:04.000Z","uid":236538,"like":9,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1d201dace48e4fd2c4e735b919d6783de3b92185","tid":1998220,"uid":236538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T08:42:14.000Z","msg":"眾所周知我地黃色經濟圈既經營者都係樂於係香港發展本土文化同產業<br />\n<br />\n我地又抱住同一樣既目標同理想 <br />\n有住同一套價值觀<br />\n<br />\n我諗每個香港人都有個概念：<br />\n覺得<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃色經濟圈=<br />\n本土真香港人既圈子</span></span><br />\n<br />\n既然係咁 我地係咪應該正名化我地本土經濟圈呢？<br />\n好似今日中聯辦咁講<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0B8pesN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0B8pesN.jpg&h=0d49267e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁如果換轉係咁樣會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MxSxono.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMxSxono.png&h=8c151813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點呀？睇完之後覺得正名化既重要性未先？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持改革 本土經濟圈<br />\n-<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黃色代表自由主義 無忘初心 繼續叫黃色經驗圈"},{"pid":"0bcb2b61dba418267caee92eaf923eac23a700e8","tid":1998220,"uid":236538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T08:42:42.000Z","msg":"留低你地既睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1001thanks"},{"pid":"4bf382fb2d6887e065b37ecd106d63257b785325","tid":1998220,"uid":2419,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T08:43:50.000Z","msg":"屌 講本土佢自然會話鳩你港獨<br />\n<br />\n所以唔洗理呢d非法機構9up"},{"pid":"b1cf13ae8d9b9e27f9e4dd6c0ec30982ef74f739","tid":1998220,"uid":353621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bf382fb2d6887e065b37ecd106d63257b785325","tid":1998220,"uid":2419,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"cited